org.jruby.runtime

Class CallBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jruby.runtime.BlockBody
      • org.jruby.runtime.CallBlock

  • public class CallBlock
extends BlockBody
    A Block implemented using a Java-based BlockCallback implementation. For lightweight block logic within Java code.
